title: Login dengan kredensial valid
steps:
1. * Buka website www.saucedemo.com
* Masukan username valid yang sudah disediakan
* Masukkan password valid yang sudah disediakan 
* Klik tombol login
steps_input_data:
1. Username valid : standar\_user
Password valid : secret\_sauce

title: Login Invalid
steps:
1. * Buka website www.saucedemo.com
* Masukan username invalid
* Masukan password invalid 
* Klik tombol login
steps_input_data:
1. username invalid: standar\_satu
password invalid: secret\_demo
steps_expected_result: 1. Muncul pesan error "Epic sadface: Username and password do to match any user in this servie"

title: Add To Cart
steps:
1. * Pilih produk 
* Klik Add to Cart 
* Buka ikon keranjang
steps_input_data: 1. Memasukan produk berupa Sace Labs Backpack

title: Checkout
steps:
1. * Klik icon Checkout
* Isi kolom Fist Name, Last Name dan Zip/Postal Code
* Klik icon Continue 
* Klik finish
steps_expected_result: 1. Mujncul pesan: "Thank you for your order" "Your order has been dispatched, and will arrive just as fast as the pony can get there!"

title: Logout
steps_expected_result: 1. Pengguna diarahkan kembali ke kahaman login
